---
import ChapterHead from "../ChapterHead.astro";
---

<div
  id="ecosystem-mapping"
  class="chapter h-full visible-page-width-disabled relative"
>
  <ChapterHead bottom={true} title="Ecosystem Mapping" height={50} />

  <div class="flex flex-col absolute top-0 left-[400px] gap-20">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-20 text-grey bg-white p-40 border-b-[30px] border-solid border-green w-[500px] min-h-[55vh]"
    >
      <span class="font-io-bold text-xl uppercase">Stakeholders</span>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <span class="font-io-regular text-lg">Primary</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-20">
            <div
              class="border-2 w-40 h-40 min-w-40 min-h-40 rounded-full bg-blue"
            >
            </div>
            <span
              >Elderly people living alone in Kortrijk and Ghent who are over 65
              years old, not very tech-savvy, and often feel lonely.</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <span class="font-io-regular text-lg">Secondary</span>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-20">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-20">
            <div
              class="w-40 h-40 min-w-40 min-h-40 rounded-full bg-orange flex justify-center items-center text-2xl"
            >
              1
            </div>
            <span
              >Individuals who interact with the city flower bed devices,
              younger and more tech-savvy, who can send voice memos to the
              elderly through the city tulip.</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-20">
            <div
              class="w-40 h-40 min-w-40 min-h-40 rounded-full bg-orange flex justify-center items-center text-2xl"
            >
              2
            </div>
            <span
              >Relatives or close acquaintances who use the mobile app to
              communicate directly with the home tulip users.</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-20">
            <div
              class="w-40 h-40 min-w-40 min-h-40 rounded-full bg-orange flex justify-center items-center text-2xl"
            >
              3
            </div>
            <span
              >Local Government and Community Organizers: Might be involved in
              the placement and maintenance of the city flower beds.</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row gap-20">
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-10">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 min-w-20 min-h-20 rounded-full bg-green">
              </div>
              <span>Touchpoints</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-10">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 min-w-20 min-h-20 rounded-full bg-grey">
              </div>
              <span>Interactions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-10">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 min-w-20 min-h-20 rounded-full bg-pink">
              </div>
              <span>Barriers</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-blue">
      <span class="font-io-bold text-xl uppercase mb-20 block">Channels</span>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <span
          >Physical Locations: City flower beds located in public areas in
          Kortrijk and Ghent.</span
        >
        <span>Digital Platforms: The mobile app for smartphones</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute -right-80 top-1/2 translate-y-[-120%] text-orange w-[450px]"
  >
    <span class="font-io-bold text-xl uppercase mb-20 block"
      >Outcomes/Goals</span
    >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
      <span
        >Reduced loneliness: With more communication we aim to reduce feelings
        of isolation among the elderly.</span
      >
      <span
        >Increased community -feeling: We encourage interaction between
        different age groups.</span
      >
      <span>
        Better monitoring and support: With the app family members can support
        the elderly userâ€™s well-being.
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <img
    class="parallax-plane-1-ecosystem-mapping absolute left-[920px] w-[750px] top-1/2 translate-y-[-50%]"
    src="./ecosystem-mapping.svg"
  />
</div>
<style>
  #ecosystem-mapping {
    @apply min-w-[1960px];
  }
</style>
